Buttons:
    Reset view - Reset to the original view
    Set view   - Set the view to a specific position and size
    Backward   - Go to the previous view (if there is one)
    Forward    - Go to the next view (if there is one)

    Play/Pause - Start/Stop iteration every frame
    Step       - Iterate a number of times
    Step Amount- The amount to step per click

    Save       - Save the current view as an image (or video?)

Events:
    Mouse - Draw box, zoom to that position
